description: Isle of Man residents should not travel to the UK while lockdowns are in place, the chief minister says.
title: Coronavirus: Manx 'should not visit UK without pressing reason'
title_page: Coronavirus: Manx 'should not visit UK without pressing reason' - BBC News
maintext: He added that patient transfers to UK hospitals would continue while restrictions were in place locally, and those travelling back to the island from the UK, such as returning students, would still be able to do so.
